[{"id":"VH978553","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure presents two perpendicular long straight wires, one vertical and the other horizontal. The horizontal wire carries a current i to the left. The vertical wire carries a current i upward. A point P is indicated. Point P is a distance d to the right of the vertical wire and a distance d above the horizontal wire.\" height=\"230\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH978553.g03.png\" width=\"400\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Two long, straight wires are perpendicular to each other but not in electrical contact. The current in each wire has magnitude <span class=\"formatted_text font_style:italic\">I</span> and direction as shown in the figure above. Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>P</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is at a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"d\"><math alttext=\"d\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>d</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> from each wire. The total magnetic field at <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>P</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> due to the currents in the wires is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B sub 0\"><math alttext=\"B sub 0\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>. At a later time, the current through one of the wires is doubled. Which of the following expressions is the magnitude of the new total magnetic field at <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>P</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH978553_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"one half B sub 0\"><math alttext=\"one half B sub 0\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><msub><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B sub 0\"><math alttext=\"B sub 0\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"three halves B sub 0\"><math alttext=\"three halves B sub 0\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><msub><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 B sub 0\"><math alttext=\"2 B sub 0\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>2</mn><msub><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3 B sub 0\"><math alttext=\"3 B sub 0\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>3</mn><msub><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":2}]